summary: An ordinance accepting deeds for street and alley purposes, and easements for slope purposes, from Manford R. Lovelett and others, for the east 10 feet of the south 53 feet of Tract 11, Gilsons Ballard Acre Tracts, and other properties, and laying off 14th Avenue Northwest, West 99th Street, East 133rd Street, 26th Avenue Northeast, East 96th Street and a public alley.
